<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 01 Mar 2024 09:13:07 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>Grifols表示尽职调查已完成，上海莱士股权出售将继续进行</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/grifols-says-due-diligence-done-shanghai-raas-stake-sale-go-ahead-2024-03-01/</link><description>西班牙制药商 Grifols 周五表示，在尽职调查程序“令人满意”结束后，该公司将继续以 18 亿美元出售上海莱士 20% 的股份。</description><pubDate>Fri, 01 Mar 2024 08:20:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/grifols-says-due-diligence-done-shanghai-raas-stake-sale-go-ahead-2024-03-01/</guid></item><item><title>要点五：永远不会有沉闷的时刻</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/take-five/global-markets-themes-takealook-2024-03-01/</link><description>美国就业数据、美联储主席的证词、美国大选日历中的一个关键日期以及总统乔·拜登的国情咨文演讲都在一周内完成。</description><pubDate>Fri, 01 Mar 2024 07:46:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/take-five/global-markets-themes-takealook-2024-03-01/</guid></item><item><title>投资者抢购“Magnificent 7”科技股和加密货币 - 美国银行</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/investors-swarm-into-tech-stocks-crypto-bofa-2024-03-01/</link><description>美国银行全球研究部周五发布的一份报告显示，截至周三的一周，投资者向科技股投入的资金达到了自 8 月以来的最高水平，并且投资加密货币的金额增加了一倍。</description><pubDate>Fri, 01 Mar 2024 07:34:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/investors-swarm-into-tech-stocks-crypto-bofa-2024-03-01/</guid></item><item><title>独家：消息人士称德意志银行将对中国开发商世茂提起清算诉讼</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/deutsche-bank-file-liquidation-suit-against-chinese-developer-shimao-sources-say-2024-03-01/</link><description>两位消息人士称，德意志银行正准备在香港对中国开发商世茂集团提起清算诉讼，这是一家外国公司在信贷违约上升和中国房地产业危机加深之际采取的罕见举措。</description><pubDate>Fri, 01 Mar 2024 06:52:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/deutsche-bank-file-liquidation-suit-against-chinese-developer-shimao-sources-say-2024-03-01/</guid></item><item><title>中国人大将于下周推出更多刺激措施，但不太可能进行大胆改革</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-parliament-unveil-more-stimulus-next-week-bold-reforms-unlikely-2024-03-01/</link><description>预计中国人大将在周二开始的年度会议上公布温和的刺激计划，以稳定增长，但可能会让那些呼吁制定大胆政策详细路线图以解决该国深度结构性失衡的人感到失望。</description><pubDate>Fri, 01 Mar 2024 06:10:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-parliament-unveil-more-stimulus-next-week-bold-reforms-unlikely-2024-03-01/</guid></item><item><title>由于美国通胀放缓，金价徘徊在一个月高点附近</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/gold-hovers-near-one-month-peak-slowing-us-inflation-2024-03-01/</link><description>周五金价徘徊在一个月高点附近，此前数据显示美国价格压力有所缓解，让投资者对美联储六月降息感到放心。</description><pubDate>Fri, 01 Mar 2024 05:08:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/gold-hovers-near-one-month-peak-slowing-us-inflation-2024-03-01/</guid></item><item><title>价格战升级 特斯拉在华推出新激励措施</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/tesla-rolls-out-new-incentives-china-price-war-escalates-2024-03-01/</link><description>特斯拉周五推出了包括保险补贴在内的新激励措施，以吸引全球最大汽车市场的消费者，这家美国电动汽车巨头正在与比亚迪等根深蒂固的竞争对手进行旷日持久的价格战。</description><pubDate>Fri, 01 Mar 2024 04:38:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/tesla-rolls-out-new-incentives-china-price-war-escalates-2024-03-01/</guid></item><item><title>恒大董事长第二座被扣押的香港豪宅挂牌出售</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/evergrande-chairmans-second-seized-hong-kong-mansion-put-up-sale-2024-03-01/</link><description>据房地产经纪人第一太平戴维斯称，曾经属于中国恒大集团董事长的香港第二座豪宅已被接管人挂牌出售。</description><pubDate>Fri, 01 Mar 2024 03:43:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/evergrande-chairmans-second-seized-hong-kong-mansion-put-up-sale-2024-03-01/</guid></item><item><title>随着中国和日本的步履蹒跚，亚洲工厂为增长而苦苦挣扎</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/wrapup-asias-factories-struggle-growth-japan-falters-china-unsteady-2024-03-01/</link><description>2月份，亚洲主要制造业经济体艰难摆脱衰退，其中日本尤其受到需求急剧下降的挤压，而中国复苏的不平衡掩盖了该地区其他地区的一些改善迹象。</description><pubDate>Fri, 01 Mar 2024 03:10:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/wrapup-asias-factories-struggle-growth-japan-falters-china-unsteady-2024-03-01/</guid></item><item><title>随着中国收紧就职前的挤压，台湾面临持续的“滴水”压力</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-faces-steady-drip-pressure-china-tightens-pre-inauguration-squeeze-2024-03-01/</link><description>在下一任总统五月就职之前，台湾正面临着来自中国的持续“滴滴”压力，台北官员担心北京可能会在不诉诸直接冲突的情况下进一步挤压台湾的回旋余地。</description><pubDate>Fri, 01 Mar 2024 02:59:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-faces-steady-drip-pressure-china-tightens-pre-inauguration-squeeze-2024-03-01/</guid></item><item><title>投资者寄希望于降息，股市上涨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-03-01/</link><description>周五，全球股市上涨，美国消费者价格数据未出现令人意外的情况，保持了央行未来几个月降息的希望。</description><pubDate>Fri, 01 Mar 2024 02:17:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-03-01/</guid></item><item><title>中国工厂活动连续五个月萎缩，加大刺激力度</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-feb-factory-activity-shrinks-5th-month-adding-pressure-economy-2024-03-01/</link><description>周五的一项官方调查显示，中国2月份制造业活动连续第五个月萎缩，在人大准备下周举行的重要年度会议之际，加大了北京方面推出更多刺激措施的压力。</description><pubDate>Fri, 01 Mar 2024 01:50:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-feb-factory-activity-shrinks-5th-month-adding-pressure-economy-2024-03-01/</guid></item><item><title>交易员权衡美联储降息押注，美元持稳；日元兑 150/dlr 走势不稳定</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-steady-traders-ponder-fed-rate-cut-bets-yen-shaky-150dlr-2024-03-01/</link><description>周五数据显示美国通胀仍然粘性但正在逐步放缓，这让人们对美联储将在 6 月开始降息的希望依然存在，而日元则跌回 150 兑美元的关键水平，周五美元保持稳定。</description><pubDate>Fri, 01 Mar 2024 01:35:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-steady-traders-ponder-fed-rate-cut-bets-yen-shaky-150dlr-2024-03-01/</guid></item><item><title>澳大利亚 Syrah Resources 与韩国 Posco Future M 签署承购协议</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/australias-syrah-resources-inks-offtake-deal-with-s-koreas-posco-future-m-2024-02-29/</link><description>澳大利亚Syrah Resources周五表示，将向韩国化学和电池材料制造商Posco Future M供应莫桑比克Balama石墨业务的天然石墨产品。</description><pubDate>Thu, 29 Feb 2024 22:08:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/australias-syrah-resources-inks-offtake-deal-with-s-koreas-posco-future-m-2024-02-29/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：市场活跃，但中国 PMI 等待公布</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-02-29/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Thu, 29 Feb 2024 21:48:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-02-29/</guid></item></channel></rss>